page.name: The Traitor
page.description: Sek-Duat XV has sent you to meet with a member of the rebellion who has decided to turn traitor. You have to stop the turncoat if you can!

properties.name: The Traitor
properties.description: Sek-Duat XV has sent you to meet with a member of the rebellion who has decided to turn traitor. You have to stop the turncoat if you can!
properties.complete: Kasuf vanishes into the desert, looking defeated and full of regret. That was a close call, but the rebellion is safe, thanks to you. Why did Sek-Duat send you instead of Zhoom? What does he have up his sleeve?

page.name: Anubis Burial Mask
page.description: This item requires a Dragon Amulet. This helm was taken from the cursed temple of the Anubis Knight. It's a little hard to breathe under the mask but then again it was meant to go on a dead guy.
